<p align="center">
	<span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span style="font-size: 36px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>Lux&middot;u&middot;ry</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p align="center">
	&nbsp;</p>
<p align="center">
	<span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span style="font-size: 22px;"><sup><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">&quot;The state of great comfort and extravagant living.&quot;</span></sup></span></span></p>
<p align="center">
	&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 22px;"><sup>Just minutes away from the Miami International Airport, Luxury Car Rentals Miami offers the finest line of luxury automobiles to enjoy Miami&rsquo;s legendary Ocean Drive and exciting South Beach. Experience unparalleled customer service in your choice of our top of the line dream cars. Our wide selection of vehicle brands include Aston Martin, Audi, Bentley, BMW, Mercedes Benz, Ferrari, Lamborghini, McLaren, Mini Cooper, Jaguar, Cadillac,&nbsp;Land Rover, Hummer, Porsche, Corvette and many more.</sup></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
	&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 22px;"><sup>Ask for our in-house Concierge and receive personalized service like VIP access to Miami&rsquo;s most exclusive nightclubs and hottest local hang-outs. That&rsquo;s only the beginning, with our network of preferred partners across South Florida, our staff will cater to your every request. We will deliver the vehicle to your doorstep, detailed, fueled and ready for you or that special someone in your life. Our goal is for our clients to enjoy an unforgettable Miami exotic car rental experience. At Luxury Car Rentals Miami, we strive to meet and exceed your expectations.</sup></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
	&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 22px;"><sup>Whether you have the exhilarating Lamborghini Aventador or elegant Cadillac Escalade delivered to you, we understand that Luxury is not just a<span> word, it&rsquo;s an experience.</span></sup></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
